#

Dijon Vinaigrette

5 min
$1.5
80 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

French

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

Salad DressingQuickEasy

Description

A tangy and zesty dressing that elevates any salad with its simple yet bold flavors.

Ingredients

  • dijon mustard: 2 tablespoons
  • red wine vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1/4 cup
  • honey: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
